Hello,
Since "Direct booting from floppy is no longer supported", this patch is
to remove the bootsect_helper code. And also a comment fix.
-- 
Coywolf Qi Hunt
Admin of 
http://GreatCN.org
 and 
http://LoveCN.org
--- setup.S.orig	Sat Mar  6 23:49:33 2004
+++ setup.S	Sun Mar  7 04:38:08 2004
